    <string name="about_description_title">About This App</string>
    <string name="about_description">This application allows you to explore NASA\'s Astronomy Picture of the Day (APOD). Each day, NASA features a different image or photograph of our fascinating universe, along with a brief explanation written by a professional astronomer.</string>
